{"tid":2110604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨Mark Simon: 香港「抗爭派」好有勇氣","createTime":"2020-07-16T04:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T12:42:30.000Z","uid":134071,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd057f4762c990f51e60cfe25fd8a787e745609","tid":2110604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"Mark Simon係黎智英助手兼共和黨成員。 黎智英能夠會見美國副總統Mike Pence， 都係Mark Simon安排。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨Mark Simon: <br />\n- 香港「抗爭派」好有勇氣, 而且很了解佢地要面對既對手 (中共).<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1283367821628469250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1283367821628469250&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n33hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=70fa1cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1283367821628469250&h=d47a5b99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1283367821628469250</a>"},{"pid":"3670d080b4de0e39fe97f5d1f0390030437a562f","tid":2110604,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"Mark Simon係黎智英助手兼共和黨成員。 黎智英能夠會見美國副總統Mike Pence， 都係Mark Simon安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190906/china-hong-kong-protests/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20190906%2Fchina-hong-kong-protests%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n33hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=ced13467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190906/china-hong-kong-protests/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n其中一個引起注意的面孔是香港傳媒大亨黎智英(Jimmy Lai)的高級助手馬克&middot;西蒙(Mark Simon)，大陸對黎智英厭惡至極。西蒙曾在美國海軍服役，今年7月，他幫助安排了黎智英與副總統彭斯的見面，引發了中國的正式外交抗議。"},{"pid":"04b7e0a11e30bed951e73b4a5052d92c5583d5e0","tid":2110604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c642eacc191520bd570d16de6009a851c62a3e","tid":2110604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:47:35.000Z","msg":"美國佬送咁大頂高帽, 都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c64e3c5c18bb493e23ad20b82236713b75888a","tid":2110604,"uid":300332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5a342f13c95702c368a95d6d318a2b76a00b11","tid":2110604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c64e3c5c18bb493e23ad20b82236713b75888a","tid":2110604,"uid":300332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69f8653b7fbad2047bffabbcda421792ec3d978","tid":2110604,"uid":357030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ef2cd622dcfe99bd063827d5a052bed7488bc9","tid":2110604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69f8653b7fbad2047bffabbcda421792ec3d978","tid":2110604,"uid":357030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree